default.text:
'Trilogy Bronze Mice'

In Referendum 211 the community voted on whether to reset the Pichiu Parachain in order to fix bugs. The underlying proposal of this Referendum has also been replaced by Referendum 205. Since Referendum 205 has passed community vote already, this Referendum (like Referendum 209) was superfluous too.

Artist: LokiKot(@LokiPages)
